snippet.title: Kore Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A Teaser Trailer for the upcoming third person stealth game - Kore

The game follows Persephone's journey through the New Orleans inspired Underworld, as she searches for Hades in a dangerous and new world. Can you make it past the lost souls and pitfalls of the underworld without becoming stuck there yourself?
